what the fuck do you want me to do?

264
00:17:45,032 --> 00:17:46,863
I can't make shit up, can I?

265
00:17:49,636 --> 00:17:51,399
It is what it is.

266
00:17:51,438 --> 00:17:53,372
If I send the surveillance teams back,

267
00:17:53,407 --> 00:17:56,570
don't come crying for more
manpower tomorrow, you hear?

268
00:17:57,678 --> 00:17:59,509
Shit is like a war, ain't it?

269
00:17:59,546 --> 00:18:01,878
Easy to get in, hell to get out.

270
00:18:21,535 --> 00:18:25,562
Pearlman knows everything. Daniels, too.
They figured it out.

271
00:18:25,606 --> 00:18:27,904
- How?
- I don't know.

272
00:18:29,409 --> 00:18:31,877
- Jesus. What are they?
- I don't know.

273
00:18:32,646 --> 00:18:36,013
She made it clear there are not to be
any further homeless killings.

274
00:18:36,049 --> 00:18:38,040
Nothing more on this case whatsoever.

275
00:18:38,085 --> 00:18:42,647
- Does she know about Marlo, that our case?
- She knows everything. Daniels knows.

276
00:18:44,024 --> 00:18:46,458
They went to the E.C.U.,
dialed up the wiretap number

277
00:18:46,493 --> 00:18:49,155
and up pops Marlo's cellphone.

278
00:18:49,196 --> 00:18:51,721
Why aren't we fired?
Why aren't we in fucking bracelets?

279
00:18:51,765 --> 00:18:53,392
I don't know.

280
00:18:54,167 --> 00:18:55,998
Oh shit, Lester.

281
00:18:57,304 --> 00:19:00,762
We gotta get outta here.
We gotta think this thing through.

282
00:19:00,807 --> 00:19:02,297
Jesus fucking Christ.

283
00:19:02,342 --> 00:19:05,641
Look, meet me down at Kavanagh's
in ten minutes, all right?

284
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:42,075
How much?

285
00:19:48,055 --> 00:19:49,317
200.

286
00:19:49,356 --> 00:19:52,484
Damn, boy. Teacher must love your black ass.

287
00:19:52,526 --> 00:19:56,895
C'mon with it. They gonna put out testers
