289
00:20:09,376 --> 00:20:11,207
C'mon, boy. C'mon.

290
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,354
Deputy.

291
00:20:54,054 --> 00:20:55,885
To be continued.

292
00:21:00,427 --> 00:21:03,487
- Fuck, fuck, fucking fuck.
- What's the matter?

293
00:21:03,530 --> 00:21:06,158
Cottage cheese for lunch
again there, Carl?

294
00:21:07,968 --> 00:21:11,233
Just because it happened
doesn't mean it's news.

295
00:21:12,305 --> 00:21:15,468
There's always a salmonella outbreak
