307
00:21:41,802 --> 00:21:43,463
We're just an afterthought.

308
00:21:43,503 --> 00:21:45,767
Whiting can smell the public service Pulitzer?

309
00:21:45,806 --> 00:21:48,206
- Seems so.
- You get a chance yet?

310
00:21:48,241 --> 00:21:50,505
Yeah, yeah. I read it.

311
00:21:50,544 --> 00:21:52,102
