and grand jury us.

338
00:23:03,183 --> 00:23:05,674
We could still go to jail and, if not,

339
00:23:05,719 --> 00:23:09,314
I expect to be back in the pawn shop unit
and you are gonna ride the boat.

340
00:23:09,356 --> 00:23:11,449
So what? It was worth it.

341
00:23:12,926 --> 00:23:14,587
Wasn't it?

342
00:23:15,128 --> 00:23:16,789
Depends.

343
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:19,731
Are they gonna let the case against Marlo
and his people stand,

344
00:23:19,766 --> 00:23:21,495
