345
00:23:21,534 --> 00:23:24,230
Why wouldn't they? It still works
on the seizures and cellphones.

346
00:23:24,271 --> 00:23:27,468
- It works without the illegal tap.
- Yeah, it does.

347
00:23:27,507 --> 00:23:29,907
And they made a big deal
about dropping Marlo.

348
00:23:29,943 --> 00:23:32,673
They called that press conference
and linked him to all the bodies.

349
00:23:32,712 --> 00:23:34,907
For them to drop the case now...

350
00:23:35,348 --> 00:23:37,111
You know, you think about it,

351
00:23:38,151 --> 00:23:41,143
we've got almost as much
on them as they do on us.

352
00:23:42,989 --> 00:23:44,149
That Tom Wolfe wannabe

353
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:46,954
thinks he's gonna
get a phrase like that past me?

354
00:23:46,993 --> 00:23:49,018
No fuckin' way, motherfucker.

355
00:23:55,201 --> 00:23:58,227
It's like a sweater with
the threads hanging off.

356
00:23:58,271 --> 00:24:00,296
Pull any thread...

357
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:03,070
Mostly exaggerations and too-perfect quotes,

358
00:24:03,109 --> 00:24:04,599
