361
00:24:09,783 --> 00:24:11,842
You know what the city
housing commissioner told me

362
00:24:11,885 --> 00:24:13,978
about the quotes in the flipping story?

363
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:18,013
He wished he'd said some of them
but that he'd never been that smart in his life.

364
00:24:18,658 --> 00:24:21,559
Someone takes the time to...

365
00:24:21,594 --> 00:24:23,619
