366
00:24:24,431 --> 00:24:26,490
What're you gonna do?

367
00:24:26,533 --> 00:24:29,058
I don't know, Robert. I don't know.

368
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:31,765
Keep my name out of it.

369
00:24:42,182 --> 00:24:43,774
No bail.

370
00:24:43,817 --> 00:24:47,753
They're claiming a propensity for violence
and witness intimidation at the bail review,

371
00:24:47,787 --> 00:24:49,482
