391
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:49,871
and word of that might have
slipped out. That's possible.

392
00:25:49,916 --> 00:25:52,077
If you were wholesaling all over town...

393
00:25:52,118 --> 00:25:56,350
They only grab your cells when they arrest you
and then they have to go get warrants

394
00:25:56,389 --> 00:25:58,721
before they can look at
the photos on the phones.

395
00:25:58,758 --> 00:26:00,817
And it's only when they get to the photos

396
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:03,260
and break the code that they have enough

397
00:26:03,296 --> 00:26:05,924
to type a charging document
for you or Chris, right?

398
00:26:05,965 --> 00:26:07,990
I mean, you aren't caught with drugs.

399
00:26:09,369 --> 00:26:13,669
But they had the arrest warrants on both of you
within a couple hours.

400
00:26:13,706 --> 00:26:17,437
Which means that they broke
the code almost instantly,

401
00:26:17,477 --> 00:26:18,876
no time at all.

402
00:26:19,312 --> 00:26:21,041
They wiretapped me.

403
00:26:21,081 --> 00:26:23,675
My investigator thinks so.

404
00:26:23,716 --> 00:26:27,447
But he doesn't know for sure
which unit ran the tap or who manned it.

405
00:26:28,788 --> 00:26:30,449
It doesn't add up.

406
00:26:38,164 --> 00:26:40,189
You gettin' out.

407
00:26:40,233 --> 00:26:42,098
You ain't.

408
00:26:43,336 --> 00:26:46,362
You hit the streets, you round up
as much muscle as possible

409
00:26:46,406 --> 00:26:48,397
and get that boy.

410
00:26:48,441 --> 00:26:50,375
He did Snoop 'cause he knew we was on him.

411
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:53,743
He knew we was on him 'cause
he the one talked about the re-up.

412
00:26:56,182 --> 00:26:58,480
Get your shit together, man.

413
00:26:58,518 --> 00:27:00,383
The bondsman came in with Levy.

414
00:27:01,087 --> 00:27:03,021
A'ight. I'm on it.

415
00:27:14,567 --> 00:27:16,592
Man, you got a dollar?

416
00:27:17,770 --> 00:27:19,431
C'mon.

417
00:27:43,696 --> 00:27:45,561
Pal.

418
00:27:49,869 --> 00:27:51,530
Pal, you all right?

419
00:27:53,339 --> 00:27:55,239
OK, here it comes,

420
00:27:55,742 --> 00:27:58,575
the dreaded crab claw.

421
00:27:59,879 --> 00:28:02,848
You know what happens
when crab claw goes...

422
00:28:04,017 --> 00:28:06,383
- It's all crab tonight...
- No crab claw!

423
00:28:06,419 --> 00:28:08,444
Yes, crab claw!

424
00:28:08,488 --> 00:28:11,321
Yeah! Crab claw does it again. Six!

425
00:28:12,091 --> 00:28:13,991
Six and I'm out...

426
00:28:16,930 --> 00:28:18,727
Yeah.

427
00:28:19,666 --> 00:28:21,258
Where?

428
00:28:22,302 --> 00:28:23,894
You're fucking kidding me.

429
00:28:23,937 --> 00:28:25,996
It's more bull...

430
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:28,007
It's bogus, Jay. I'm telling you...

431
00:28:32,912 --> 00:28:34,675
OK.

432
00:28:35,949 --> 00:28:37,610
I gotta go.

433
00:28:39,219 --> 00:28:41,653
I have to keep running the string out.
I've no choice.

434
00:28:41,688 --> 00:28:43,713
You said the bosses know.

435
00:28:44,624 --> 00:28:48,720
Some do, some don't. The ones that do
want us to keep pretending.

436
00:28:48,761 --> 00:28:50,661
We stop pretending, then...

437
00:28:53,066 --> 00:28:55,899
Listen, we'll finish this tomorrow night, OK?

438
00:28:57,570 --> 00:28:59,299
I'll see you in a bit.

439
00:29:09,215 --> 00:29:10,944
What do you think?

440
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:15,713
I mean, puttin' my shit in the streets?

441
00:29:18,691 --> 00:29:20,488
Well, it's you.

442
00:29:20,994 --> 00:29:22,859
He's got you.

443
00:29:22,895 --> 00:29:24,624
Yeah, well.

444
00:29:24,664 --> 00:29:26,632
I mean he's got what you're about.

445
00:29:27,533 --> 00:29:30,400
The guy likes you,
that shows through.

446
00:29:30,436 --> 00:29:34,167
I mean, you know, he's saying
this giving back that you're doing,

447
00:29:34,207 --> 00:29:36,903
he's putting that up against Sherrod.

448
00:29:36,943 --> 00:29:39,207
He ain't lettin' you
off the hook for shit

449
00:29:39,245 --> 00:29:42,214
but he's just puttin' it all out there.

450
00:29:42,248 --> 00:29:44,239
You know, the good and the bad.

451
00:29:44,284 --> 00:29:46,184
You know what?

452
00:29:47,854 --> 00:29:50,254
The bad don't bother me to have out there.

453
00:29:50,290 --> 00:29:53,851
Shit, I know the bad.
I ain't lyin' to no one about the bad.

454
00:29:54,894 --> 00:29:57,419
Scared of somebody callin' you good?

455
00:29:59,766 --> 00:30:03,258
A lot of folks volunteer places.
A lot of folks share at meetings.

456
00:30:03,303 --> 00:30:06,500
Plenty of motherfuckers wake up every day
and not get high.

457
00:30:06,539 --> 00:30:10,168
Man makin' me sound special
for doin' what the fuck I need to be doin'.

458
00:30:13,746 --> 00:30:15,475
Read it.

459
00:30:24,290 --> 00:30:26,758
"You can hold back
from the suffering of the world,

460
00:30:26,793 --> 00:30:28,784
"you have free permission to do so

461
00:30:28,828 --> 00:30:31,262
"and it is in accordance with your nature.

462
00:30:32,465 --> 00:30:34,330
"But perhaps this very holding back

463
00:30:34,367 --> 00:30:36,961
"is the one suffering you could have avoided."

464
00:30:37,970 --> 00:30:39,733
Fran-zee Kafka.

465
00:30:40,373 --> 00:30:41,965
Who's he?

466
00:30:42,008 --> 00:30:44,101
Some writer.

467
00:30:44,143 --> 00:30:46,077
You read his books?

468
00:30:46,112 --> 00:30:48,672
Fuck no. But you remember Flubber?

469
00:30:49,782 --> 00:30:53,047
He handed that to me
the night that he had me start leading

470
00:30:53,086 --> 00:30:55,077
the Saint Martin meeting.

471
00:30:56,122 --> 00:30:58,249
I kept it ever since.

472
00:30:59,525 --> 00:31:01,425
What it mean to you?

473
00:31:05,231 --> 00:31:07,028
You want these?

474
00:31:07,066 --> 00:31:10,797
Yeah, my man say he need it back
and not to make any copies.

475
00:31:12,004 --> 00:31:15,770
He say he ain't supposed to show it to me
before it goes in the paper.

476
00:31:15,808 --> 00:31:17,537
I mean, if I let him.

477
00:31:17,577 --> 00:31:19,169
You gonna?

478
00:31:22,849 --> 00:31:24,840
Thanks for the crabs.

479
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,823
Gray van.

480
00:31:32,925 --> 00:31:35,894
- You get the tag?
- I couldn't see it from where I was.

481
00:31:35,928 --> 00:31:38,260
